Class BigNumberImpl

java.lang.Object
bignumber.BigNumberImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:
BigNumber, Comparable<BigNumber>
public class BigNumberImpl extends Object implements BigNumber
The BigNumberImpl class represents a non-negative number of arbitrary lengths.
